body: The test driver got stale. It's been belatedly updated to 2019.3. It needs to be updated more frequently.

comment_data.body: Android Studio 4.0 is still based on 2019.3. When 4.1 is the stable release we can do this. Probably 4Q20.

We are currently using Junit 4.13. The latest version is 4.13.1, from Oct 2020. We'll have to wait a bit longer to do this.
[https://junit.org/junit4/](https://junit.org/junit4/)
IntelliJ isn't ready for junit 5 yet.

milestone.description: Issues under consideration for upcoming milestones.
milestone.title: On Deck

title: Update junit test driver when 2020.1 is stable
